@sparerd  - I haven't looked at the cred repo stuff since before it was initially pulled out, so I don't recall... But does it store all credential records individually or can you have user/password pairs that are selectable?

For example, if I use the super secure combination of "user" and "password" across 5 hosts, would I have 5 separate records tied to each of the 5 hosts, or 1 credential record that is used by all 5 hosts?

If it's the later, then there would need to be some adjustments...
